data.description:
Introducing this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bath residence with a den, where elegance meets modern comfort. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers a perfect blend of luxurious features and thoughtful design. 

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the abundance of natural light that bathes the spacious open floor plan. The interior boasts beautiful plank flooring throughout, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere. The neutral color palette enhances the sense of tranquility and allows you to add your personal touch effortlessly. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring sleek stainless steel appliances that any chef would adore. With ample counter space and storage, meal preparation and entertaining are a breeze. The adjacent dining area seamlessly flows into the living room, making it an ideal space for gatherings with family and friends.

Plantation shutters adorn the windows, offering both style and functionality, allowing you to control the amount of natural light and privacy to your liking. 

When you're ready to relax and unwind, step outside to your private oasis. The backyard showcases a refreshing pool, perfect for cooling off on hot summer days, while the lush green grass area provides a serene setting for outdoor activities and leisure.

With 4 bedrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone to have their own retreat. The den can be transformed into a home office, library, or even a fifth bedroom, providing versatility to suit your needs.

This property is the epitome of comfort, style, and functionality, offering a luxurious living experience that you'll be proud to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable residence your own.
